"Ever since you were young and gazed upon the great steam engines of your "
"city's local industrial district, you've dreamed of mastering the complex "
"world behind materials and their motion. After years of devotion, you "
"achieved your dream and became well versed in the mechanical sciences."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Profession (female Engineer of Mechanics) description
